          "DETECTOR": [
            {
              "pointer": "",
              "coded_information": [
                "TELES",
                "HPGE",
                "SI"
              ],
              "free_text": [
                " In these two experiments, the emitted",
                "gamma-radiation and charged-particles were detected",
                "with the STARS-LIBERACE detector array, which consists",
                "of large area of segmented annular silicon detectors",
                " (dE-E telescope) and up to six HPGe Clover detectors.",
                "Five Clover germanium detectors were placed at",
                "16.5(+-0.5) cm from the target: two Clovers were",
                "located at 40., one at 90. and two at 140. degr.,",
                "relative to the beam direction.",
                "The charged-particle telescope was comprised of two",
                "Micron Semiconductor S2-type silicon detectors (22 mm",
                "active inner diameter and 70 mm active outer diameter):",
                "a 152 mum as dE detector and a 1003 mum as E detector"
              ]
            }
          ],
